item.title: CVE-2020-26205|2024-08-04T15:49:07.249Z -- salopensource -- sal
item.description: Sal is a multi-tenanted reporting dashboard for Munki with the ability to display information from Facter. In Sal through version 4.1.6 there is an XSS vulnerability on the machine_list view.
